                     <interp inst="t18390617-1985-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390617-cd-231" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390617-1985-offence-1 t18390617-cd-231"></join>21st of May</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390617-name-1457" type="victimName">
